msgid "CMAKE_DISABLE_PRECOMPILE_HEADERS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../envvar/include/ENV_VAR.rst:1
msgid ""
"This is a CMake :ref:`Environment Variable <CMake Language Environment "
"Variables>`. Its initial value is taken from the calling process environment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../envvar/CMAKE_DISABLE_PRECOMPILE_HEADERS.rst:8
msgid ""
"The default value for the :variable:`CMAKE_DISABLE_PRECOMPILE_HEADERS` "
"variable when there is no explicit configuration given on the first run "
"while creating a new build tree.  On later runs in an existing build tree "
"the value persists in the cache as :variable:"
"`CMAKE_DISABLE_PRECOMPILE_HEADERS`."
msgstr ""
